{"tid":2127843,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[熱烈祝賀]感謝慈雲山人無私爲黨國奉獻DNA！！！","createTime":"2020-07-27T14:09:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-27T18:12:20.000Z","uid":248120,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"361b48368c7c7b78eb9abbf41190a7f8754ea18e","tid":2127843,"uid":248120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T14:09:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202007/27/P2020072700401.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F202007%2F27%2FP2020072700401.htm&d=ducsj56GsZITs%2BYA0ylwpdUsrLV3ynd9sCeqRx8pZcg%3D&h=7ad58304\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202007/27/P2020072700401.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>民政事務總署（民政總署）與<strong><span class=\"red\">東華三院</span></strong>攜手合作，今日（七月二十七日）推出「2019冠狀病毒病慈雲山社區檢測計劃」（「慈雲山檢測計劃」），為慈雲山居民安排由檢測承辦商（<strong><span class=\"red\">中龍檢驗認證（香港）有限公司</span></strong>）提供的2019冠狀病毒病檢測服務。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n各位慈「黃」山街坊：<br />\n聽到免費檢測，眨下眼就慳返千零兩千大銀<br />\n大家係咪好興奮呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>好戲在後頭！</strong><br />\n<span class=\"red\">驗完DNA直送祖國懷抱<br />\n爲偉大祖國基因資料庫作無償無私奉獻<br />\n祖國既未來就靠晒你<br />\n係咪覺得自己好偉大呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.cichk.com/tc/investor/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cichk.com%2Ftc%2Finvestor%2F&d=ducsj56GsZITs%2BYA0ylwpdUsrLV3ynd9sCeqRx8pZcg%3D&h=dde2aaaf\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.cichk.com/tc/investor/</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.cichk.com/tc/about/index.php?id=18\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cichk.com%2Ftc%2Fabout%2Findex.php%3Fid%3D18&d=ducsj56GsZITs%2BYA0ylwpdUsrLV3ynd9sCeqRx8pZcg%3D&h=46114e45\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.cichk.com/tc/about/index.php?id=18</a><br />\n各位睇睇，今次爲大家驗毒既承辦商<br />\n全力支持國安法，保證絕無「黃絲暴徒」操縱結果<br />\n經黨和國家認證，十足十信心保證！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"green\">國家，會感謝你的！</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"b990f9ee610f8cff1125ee0f8c5d0ebeda4ef21a","tid":2127843,"uid":248120,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T14:17:18.000Z","msg":"中龍檢驗認證（香港）有限公司（下稱&ldquo;中龍&rdquo;）於1993年成立，是<span class=\"red\">中國檢驗有限公司</span>的檢測中心和全資子公司，是一所<del>獨立</del>、<del>公正</del>的品質檢測服務機構⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n中國檢驗有限公司是經<span class=\"red\">國務院</span>批准，於1982年在香港註冊成立的綜合性檢驗、測試、認證和鑒定機構，是<span class=\"red\">國家質檢總局、國家認監委設在香港的中資企業</span>，受國家質檢總局授權或委託開展檢驗、鑒定、認證、測試業務，並自主開發檢驗市場。目前，服務範圍已覆蓋工業產品、食品、消費品、動植物⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85f24bd4e7aee96b94f564251c60d044f139db6d","tid":2127843,"uid":248120,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T15:16:44.000Z","msg":"推爆黨既謊言！！！"},{"pid":"15f8fb1e0194f1814edc6059a677dfec6f55597c","tid":2127843,"uid":103414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T05:49:35.000Z","msg":"冇人覆你<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e89373f884ab30a5c4a25e662cb639839edf3f31","tid":2127843,"uid":103414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T05:52:12.000Z","msg":"但佢唔係強制性 驗唔驗好<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bfaefb3dc7b94c389fb0b3f891dcd0bc04cdf44","tid":2127843,"uid":203499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T06:35:34.000Z","msg":"仲諗緊驗唔驗好嘅，奉勸幾句<br />\n<br />\n你冇病癥，驗咗冇唔代表你